No. 09-8430. Raymond Payne, Petitioner v. Joseph B. Scarnati, Lieutenant Governor and Chairperson, Pennsylvania Board of Pardons, et al. 559 U.S. 988, 130 S. Ct. 1709,

176 L. Ed. 2d 207,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 1911. March 1, 2010.

Petition for writ of cer-tiorari to the Supreme Court of Pennsylvania, Western District, denied.

Justice Alito took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.

Same case below, 603 Pa. 74, 981 A.2d 1287.
